node.text:
My shop opens in a few hours! (Link in bio 💕) Calendars will come in a few sets to choose from. They will be available together with a bookmark, sticker, A4 prints (as you can see on the 3rd photo) - there are limited spots ❤️ Lots of new prints, coloring pages and stickers restocked again 🥰 I hope you’ll find something for yourself! 
Thank you so much for your interest and support! 🥺
⭐️NOTE FOR BUYERS
⁃I’ll be sending out all of your orders once the shop closes (at the end of September)! Thank you so much for your patience.
⁃Please note that the prices may change a bit at the checkout depending on the vat tax rate in your country (new vat regulations came into force in the UE that affected the price for Polish entrepreneur) 
⁃Unfortunately I wasn’t able to fix the vat shipping for the UK yet so shipping to the UK won’t be available yet 😔💔
.
.
.
#art #artist #artoftheday #artistsoninstagram #calendar #smallbusiness #cuteart #digitalart #digitalpainting #illustration #drawing #drawingoftheday #instaartist #kawaiiaesthetic

node.text:
Finally all of my monster girls are complete! ⭐️ PREORDERS for calendars and shop opening starts at 1 am CET on Sunday (12th September) ⭐️ I’ve painted 12 illustrations for this project especially ^_^ I’ll share more photos of the calendar tomorrow 😊 I’m so happy with how it turned out! It’s been more than a year since I’ve started working on this series and I’m so excited to see it completed in a calendar for the year of 2022 ❤️ Stay tuned for more info soon!
.
.
.
#art #artoftheday #artistsoninstagram #dailyart #instaartist #monsters #cuteart #artwork #digitalpainting #digitalart #illustration #girls #drawing #digitalartist

*
Download Puzzles & Survival：https://pns.onelink.me/6tpA/toshiasan
Celebrate Puzzles & Survival 1st anniversary！
*
Gift Code: toshiasan
You Get: 
Diamond*300

The outbreak of a deadly virus swept over the world. Almost all of humanity have turned into zombies. Lead your followers to survive the apocalypse: that is your quest.
Match-3 Puzzle meets Strategy! Solve the mysteries and build an impenetrable sanctuary. The future of humanity is in your hands.
Tip: Use your brain to defend your brain in Puzzles & Survival!

node.text:
Hi guys! I wanted to paint a few of monster high girls together, especially for the calendar that I will be having soon in my shop 👀💖 Hope you enjoy this illustration and I kinda wish I’ve had also included Frankie there as well but let’s just say she’s taking the photo! 🥺❤️ 
It's been such a crazy month for me and I really took a break that I needed. I think it's actually the longest break I've taken :o I really hope to be around here much more often and to bring you lots of new fun arts! Thank you for sticking around with me, I appreciate it so much! 
.
.
.
#digitalart #drawing #illustration #painting #photoshop #art #artist #artoftheday #digitaldrawing #cute #kawaii #friends #dailyart #monster

node.text:
Hi guys! Long time no new posts from me, 
I missed posting here and talking to you! 💕🥺
This is the latest illustration I painted for the winner of the @calpico.usa CALPICO new flavor contest! 
The melon flavor was chosen as their new flavor by voting from CALPICO fans at the CALPICO Contest flavor stage. I also voted for melon flavor so was super happy to draw this :D
Now they are at the bottle design stage and the design contest is starting now! 
You can submit your original CALPICO bottle design for the chance to win prizes or even possibly have your design in stores! *v*
Follow this link: https://contest2021.calpico-usa.com/package-design-contest/
to take part. You could win some awesome prizes and your design could become
available in stores next summer! 
Thank you CALPICO for hosting such awesome giveaways! ❤️
.
.
.
#calpico #digitalart #digitalpainting #digitalillustration #drawing #illustration #painting #photoshopart #art #artist #artoftheday #artistsoninstagram #kawaiiart #melon #summeroutfit

node.text:
Mermaid protecting her little birb friend 😊🌸 Okay so I’m just one day late for the Mermay party ❤️ I’m glad I managed to finished this today, also I found my Ariel drawing from a year ago that is not finished and I’m tempted to give it a second try  this year :D
.
.
